<!-- FEATURE IMAGES -->
<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:85vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/01_20241021110528A084_20250609144454A156.jpg" alt="EU5 Exterior"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Pure Electric Performance</h3><p>401km NEDC range with CATL ternary lithium battery (48.3kWh). 120kW maximum power and 240N&middot;m torque deliver strong acceleration under 10 seconds 0-100km/h. Fast charge 30%-80% in just 30 minutes.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side"><div class="feature-side-img"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/2_20220928114424A154_20250609144533A161.jpg" alt="Interior"></div><div class="feature-side-content"><h3>Intelligent Cockpit</h3><p>9-inch central control screen with mobile phone interconnection. 7-inch LCD + LED instrument panel. PU steering wheel with multi-function controls. Manual anti-glare rearview mirror and dual sun visors with vanity mirrors.</p></div></div></section>

<section class="feature-full" style="min-height:80vh"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/06/16/3_20230616115537A201.jpg" alt="Technology"><div class="feature-overlay"><h3>Advanced EV Technology</h3><p>Liquid-cooled CATL battery with 164.41 Wh/kg energy density. Single-speed EV gearbox with rotary shift and sports driving mode. Braking energy recovery system maximizes efficiency. Power consumption &le;13.7 kWh/100km.</p></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/ar 拷贝 3_20250526145819A038_20250609144546A162.jpg" alt="Safety"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Comprehensive Safety</h4><p>ESP+TCS, ABS+EBD, EBA+BA, HHC, HDC, Auto Hold, TPMS standard</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/EU5 2_20230213164409A127_20250609162028A204.jpg" alt="Comfort"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Spacious Interior</h4><p>430L cargo capacity. Rear seat integral recline. 3 rear headrests adjustable.</p></div></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-side" style="direction:rtl"><div class="feature-side-img" style="direction:ltr"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/6_20240207140809A057_20250609162104A209.jpg" alt="Charging"></div><div class="feature-side-content" style="direction:ltr"><h3>Convenient Charging</h3><p>Fast charging 30%-80% SOC in &le;30 minutes at ordinary temperature. Slow charging 0-100% in &le;9 hours. Low speed pedestrian warning and collision sensing automatic unlocking for enhanced safety.</p></div></div></section>

<section><div class="feature-duo"><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2025/06/09/7_20220927155036A075_20250526145933A048_20250609144627A167.jpg" alt="Design"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>LED Daytime Running Lights</h4><p>LED DRL, penetrating taillight, emergency braking double-flash</p></div></div><div class="feature-duo-item"><img src="https://www.baicglobal.com/file/common/image/2023/02/13/EU5 5_20230213164446A129.jpg" alt="Colors"><div class="feature-duo-ov"><h4>Six Body Colors</h4><p>Silver, Red, White, Blue, Gray, Black</p></div></div></div></section>

